<title>USA: CCA sees Q2 EPS between $0.07 and $0.09.</title>
<headline>CCA sees Q2 EPS between $0.07 and $0.09.</headline>
<dateline>EAST RUTHERFORD, N.J. 1997-06-02</dateline>
<text>
<p>CCA Industries Inc said Monday that it expects fully diluted earnings per share for the second quarter ended May 31 to total between $0.07 and $0.09.</p>
<p>The company, which distributes health and beauty aids, reported earnings of $0.04 a share for its first quarter.</p>
<p>For the second quarter last year, it made $0.06 a share.</p>
<p>CCA also said it expects second quarter sales of $11 million or 20 percent more than the first quarter.</p>
<p>For the second quarter last year, sales reached $10.5 million.</p>
